### Banking REST API - Test Endpoints
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@customerId = 1
@customerId2 = 2
@accountId = 1001
@newCustomerId = 5
@newAccountId = 1007

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ============================================
### CUSTOMER ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### 1. Get All Customers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers

### 2. Get Customer by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/{{customerId}}

### 3. Search Customers by Name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/search?name=John

### 4. Get Premium Customers (balance > $10,000)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/premium

### 5. Create New Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Williams",
  "email": "alice.williams@example.com"
}

### 6. Create Another Customer for Testing
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Michael Brown",
  "email": "michael.brown@example.com"
}

### 7. Update Customer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/{{customerId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "email": "john.doe.updated@example.com"
}

### 8. Delete Customer
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/{{customerId}}

### ============================================
### ACCOUNT ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### 9. Get All Accounts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts

### 10. Get Account by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{accountId}}

### 11. Search Accounts by Customer Name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/search?name=Jane

### 12. Create New Account
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_number": "ACC007",
  "account_type": "Savings",
  "balance": 50000.00,
  "customer_id": 1
}

### 13. Create Checking Account
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_number": "ACC008",
  "account_type": "Checking",
  "balance": 10000.00,
  "customer_id": 2
}

### 14. Update Account
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{accountId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "balance": 30000.00,
  "account_type": "Checking"
}

### 15. Delete Account
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/{{accountId}}

### ============================================
### ERROR HANDLING TESTS
### ============================================

### Test 404 - Non-existent Customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/customers/999

### Test 404 - Non-existent Account
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/999

### Test 400 - Invalid Create Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}

### Test 400 - Invalid Create Account (missing customer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_number": "ACC999",
  "account_type": "Savings",
  "balance": 1000.00
}

### Test 404 - Create Account for Non-existent Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_number": "ACC999",
  "account_type": "Savings",
  "balance": 1000.00,
  "customer_id": 999
}
